</nav></header><main aria-label="main content"><div class="speakable">
      <b data-is-speakable>While Taliban Fight On, U.S. Tries Keeping Political Deal On Track</b>   <b data-is-speakable>Afghanistan's president is resisting a promised prisoner swap, the Taliban has resumed attacks, but U.S. officials are pushing both sides to sit down for a political settlement to end the war.</b>
